Package etomica.molecule.iterator

Class MoleculeIteratorArrayListSimple

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.molecule.iterator.MoleculeIteratorArrayListSimple
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AtomsetIterator, MoleculeIterator, MoleculesetIterator, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MoleculeIteratorAllMolecules, MoleculeIteratorArrayList, MoleculeIteratorMolecule

    public class MoleculeIteratorArrayListSimple
extends java.lang.Object
implements MoleculeIterator, java.io.Serializable
    An atom iterator of the elements from an AtomArrayList (in proper sequence). Iterator will fail if element are added to or removed from list while iteration is proceeding.
